19
00:01:51,635 --> 00:01:54,015
Did I make a mistake?

20
00:01:56,735 --> 00:02:02,155
I promised Yunqian that I would protect his family.

21
00:02:03,974 --> 00:02:06,195
But who would've known?

22
00:02:08,235 --> 00:02:11,130
I could not even protect him.

23
00:02:11,130 --> 00:02:13,680
   

24
00:02:14,510 --> 00:02:16,415
You're upset with me.

25
00:02:23,654 --> 00:02:25,635
I just think that...

26
00:02:26,355 --> 00:02:28,255
if it weren't for me,

27
00:02:29,214 --> 00:02:31,294
he wouldn't have died.

28
00:02:32,795 --> 00:02:35,454
The Sun family deserved it.

29
00:02:36,174 --> 00:02:40,194
Sun Ru colluded with Zhuang Wenfeng and embezzled the disaster relief fund.

30
00:02:40,194 --> 00:02:44,514
This caused widespread starvation and millions of people were left without a home.

31
00:02:44,514 --> 00:02:47,015
Did he not deserve to die?

32
00:02:49,035 --> 00:02:53,014
As for your friend, I gave him the opportunity to live.

33
00:02:54,315 --> 00:02:56,854
But he chose to die.

34
00:03:08,154 --> 00:03:10,135
Am I wrong?

35
00:03:13,714 --> 00:03:15,214
Life is cruel.

36
00:03:15,214 --> 00:03:17,155
Who doesn't suffer?

37
00:03:17,714 --> 00:03:22,195
He was luckier than most, yet he did not appreciate it.

38
00:03:24,654 --> 00:03:26,454
It's good that he's dead.

39
00:03:26,454 --> 00:03:30,055
A weak man does not deserve to live in this world.

40
00:03:31,514 --> 00:03:33,114
Your Highness,

41
00:03:34,355 --> 00:03:36,155
do you still remember your initial goals?

42
00:03:36,155 --> 00:03:37,855
Of course.

43
00:03:38,714 --> 00:03:40,854
To become an empress,

44
00:03:40,854 --> 00:03:43,636
bring change to the corrupted government of Southern Chen,

45
00:03:43,636 --> 00:03:46,375
and make this country a better place.

46
00:03:47,334 --> 00:03:49,975
Then, is everything that you do now...

47
00:03:50,535 --> 00:03:52,934
for the sake of that goal?

48
00:03:52,934 --> 00:03:55,215
I know what you mean.

49
00:03:58,935 --> 00:04:00,835
Let me ask you.

50
00:04:02,214 --> 00:04:05,734
The life of one man and one family.

51
00:04:05,734 --> 00:04:07,794
Which matters more?

52
00:04:08,575 --> 00:04:11,475
The life of a family and a country.

53
00:04:11,475 --> 00:04:13,595
Which matters more?

54
00:04:14,714 --> 00:04:20,774
What is wrong with giving up on a man and a family for the sake of a country's people?

55
00:04:25,715 --> 00:04:29,800
Everything comes... at a price

56
00:04:29,800 --> 00:04:32,455
Both were black sheep,

57
00:04:32,455 --> 00:04:35,354
but why must Sun Ru die

58
00:04:35,354 --> 00:04:38,275
yet Zhou Cishan can live?

59
00:04:40,314 --> 00:04:42,774
It's only temporary.

60
00:04:42,774 --> 00:04:44,554
When the timing is right,

61
00:04:44,554 --> 00:04:47,030
he will receive the penalty he deserves.

62
