00:05:07,035 --> 00:05:09,234
Such a temper.

66
00:05:25,734 --> 00:05:27,434
Uncle?

67
00:05:33,074 --> 00:05:35,794
I was not expecting you, sorry for my rudeness.

68
00:05:35,794 --> 00:05:38,315
I hope you can forgive me.

69
00:05:38,315 --> 00:05:40,595
I came uninvited.

70
00:05:40,595 --> 00:05:42,575
Sorry for intruding, Your Highness.

71
00:05:42,575 --> 00:05:47,235
Do you need something from me, Uncle?

72
00:05:48,815 --> 00:05:50,654
It's nothing.

73
00:05:51,654 --> 00:05:54,615
I just wanted to speak with you.

74
00:05:55,334 --> 00:05:58,914
Please feel free. I'm all ears.

75
00:06:07,534 --> 00:06:09,835
Don't go too far.

76
00:06:12,234 --> 00:06:14,654
What do you mean, Uncle?

77
00:06:16,434 --> 00:06:19,814
The one thing your father hated most

78
00:06:19,814 --> 00:06:22,015
was to see sibling rivalry between you all.

79
00:06:22,015 --> 00:06:27,335
He wished for his children to live in peace.

80
00:06:27,335 --> 00:06:31,914
He wished to see you live in harmony

81
00:06:31,914 --> 00:06:34,035
and care for each other.

82
00:06:35,100 --> 00:06:36,900
Unfortunately,

83
00:06:37,455 --> 00:06:40,155
not everything goes according to what you wish for.

84
00:06:41,634 --> 00:06:43,334
It seems...

85
00:06:44,155 --> 00:06:46,615
that you don't plan to turn away from the wrong path.

86
00:06:46,615 --> 00:06:48,415
The wrong path?

87
00:06:49,815 --> 00:06:53,855
Uncle, what do you think is the right path?

88
00:06:53,855 --> 00:06:57,935
The right path is your father's will.

89
00:06:57,935 --> 00:07:00,155
Since he willed for Chen'er to inherit the throne,

90
00:07:00,155 --> 00:07:02,735
I will protect him at all costs.

91
00:07:03,275 --> 00:07:08,214
If anyone with ill intentions dares shake up the foundation of Southern Chen,

92
00:07:09,214 --> 00:07:12,055
I will not hold back.

93
00:07:13,514 --> 00:07:15,734
If so,

94
00:07:15,734 --> 00:07:17,934
I shall look forward to it.

95
