96
00:07:27,470 --> 00:07:29,715
Back in the day,

97
00:07:29,715 --> 00:07:33,680
you and I, along with Brother Sun,

98
00:07:33,680 --> 00:07:36,054
ranked on the honor roll together

99
00:07:36,054 --> 00:07:38,234
and toured the streets on horseback.

100
00:07:38,234 --> 00:07:41,074
We were so high-spirited.

101
00:07:41,754 --> 00:07:43,934
But in such a short time...

102
00:07:49,995 --> 00:07:52,035
But in such a short time,

103
00:07:54,235 --> 00:07:56,895
he left us eternally.

104
00:08:09,674 --> 00:08:13,034
Brother Sun had a big heart

105
00:08:13,034 --> 00:08:15,434
and held no prejudice.

106
00:08:15,434 --> 00:08:19,720
He always took extra care of me

107
00:08:19,720 --> 00:08:22,175
and I'm very grateful.

108
00:08:22,175 --> 00:08:24,074
Did you know?

109
00:08:25,194 --> 00:08:27,914
Brother Sun once told me this.

110
00:08:31,035 --> 00:08:33,574
Though he is in the ancestral hall,

111
00:08:34,515 --> 00:08:36,675
his heart is with the world.

112
00:08:40,554 --> 00:08:46,974
His biggest wish was to see the world like a wild free crane.

113
00:08:47,834 --> 00:08:50,135
And during his free time,

114
00:08:50,135 --> 00:08:54,450
to exchange drinks with close friends...

115
00:08:55,915 --> 00:08:58,275
would have been paradise.

116
00:09:00,314 --> 00:09:03,135
Indeed, he lived a solitary life.

117
00:09:05,374 --> 00:09:07,074
But...

118
00:09:09,055 --> 00:09:11,394
he mistrusted one man.

119
00:09:19,914 --> 00:09:22,214
I wasn't sure before,

120
00:09:24,454 --> 00:09:27,055
but seeing how sad you are,

121
00:09:28,354 --> 00:09:32,454
I am certain that you did not...

122
00:09:34,015 --> 00:09:36,595
intentionally cause Brother Sun's death,

123
00:09:36,595 --> 00:09:41,735
but it was the one who supported you that led it to happen.

124
00:09:43,654 --> 00:09:45,755
Brother Shen,

125
00:09:45,755 --> 00:09:49,075
do you really know Princess Roujia?

126
00:09:50,195 --> 00:09:52,294
Did you know?

127
00:09:52,294 --> 00:09:54,235
My tutor...

128
00:09:55,255 --> 00:09:57,995
also had an unnatural death.

129
00:09:59,515 --> 00:10:04,254
And the cause was your endorsement.

130
00:10:17,574 --> 00:10:19,574
I know.

131
00:10:19,574 --> 00:10:22,995
You did not intend for him to die.

132
00:10:22,995 --> 00:10:27,547
It was Princess Roujia who used you to lure me in,

133
00:10:27,547 --> 00:10:32,734
then sent men to kill my tutor then later, blamed it on the Sun family.

134
00:10:38,054 --> 00:10:41,915
But, Brother Shen, I know you may not have wanted to be part of it.

135
00:10:41,915 --> 00:10:45,415
Since you know everything so clearly,

136
00:10:45,415 --> 00:10:46,954
are you sure...

137
00:10:47,574 --> 00:10:52,315
that you will still enable such deeds for your own agenda?

138
00:11:08,335 --> 00:11:09,935
Zhuohua?

139
00:11:09,935 --> 00:11:11,754
Why are you here?

140
00:11:12,735 --> 00:11:18,435
I'm so sorry for disturbing you, Your Highness.

141
00:11:22,015 --> 00:11:26,095
My uncle said something similar, too.

142
00:11:26,095 --> 00:11:30,495
You must know why I'm here, then.

143
00:11:31,574 --> 00:11:34,234
Why are you so polite with me, Zhuohua?

144
00:11:35,015 --> 00:11:40,215
I believe that you understand why, Your Highness.

145
00:11:45,174 --> 00:11:48,874
You and I are like-minded with similar circumstances.

146
00:11:48,874 --> 00:11:52,154
We have poor relationships with our families, and are both aware...

147
00:11:52,895 --> 00:11:57,494
of how challenging our paths are as women.

148
00:11:57,494 --> 00:11:59,174
Since that is the case,

149
00:11:59,934 --> 00:12:06,054
we should be of one mind and help each other to finish this race.

150
00:12:13,694 --> 00:12:17,994
In my opinion, you're not quite right, Your Highness.

151
00:12:17,994 --> 00:12:19,754
Which part of it?

152
00:12:21,174 --> 00:12:26,574
In the beginning, I really thought that we could walk together.

153
00:12:27,855 --> 00:12:29,555
Later on,

154
00:12:30,654 --> 00:12:33,674
I thought that we just worked differently toward the same goal.

155
00:12:34,735 --> 00:12:37,074
But now, I realize...

156
00:12:39,015 --> 00:12:41,935
that we are no longer going in the same direction...

157
00:12:43,294 --> 00:12:45,275
and have parted ways.

158
00:13:13,774 --> 00:13:15,675
Our relationship...

159
00:13:17,654 --> 00:13:19,694
is just like this hairpin.

160
00:13:32,615 --> 00:13:35,094
Since she does not appreciate my kindness,

161
00:13:36,975 --> 00:13:39,454
then I will not hold back.

162
