00:14:07,414 --> 00:14:12,014
 Your Highness, what kind of person are you? 

165
00:14:16,100 --> 00:14:19,870
♫  A dream of a goose and a phoenix crossing together  ♫

166
00:14:19,870 --> 00:14:22,839
♫  Tenderness is like parting and complaints  ♫

