♫  Going around for a lifetime, constantly cut and scattered, 
 the world is day and night  ♫

168
00:14:30,139 --> 00:14:34,550
♫  The fireworks of the world are like quicksand 
 of the world after all  ♫

169
00:14:34,550 --> 00:14:36,233
 - Your Highness. 
 - I'm sorry. 

170
00:14:36,233 --> 00:14:38,034
 - Are you okay? 
 - Thank you. 

171
00:14:38,034 --> 00:14:41,654
 Thank you, Your Highness. 

172
00:14:41,654 --> 00:14:43,935
 I'm not worthy of your thanks. 

173
00:14:43,935 --> 00:14:46,014
 The world owes it to you. 

174
00:14:46,015 --> 00:14:48,735
 Nobody is less worthy than others. 

175
00:14:49,560 --> 00:14:51,173
♫  Again, someone on the precipice of fate  ♫

176
00:14:51,174 --> 00:14:53,733
 Which is the real you? 

177
00:14:53,733 --> 00:15:01,360
♫  The heartache is caused by the painful loneliness  ♫

178
00:15:10,095 --> 00:15:11,915
Brother Yunqian,

179
00:15:13,694 --> 00:15:15,834
are you willing...

180
00:15:18,335 --> 00:15:23,674
to get drunk with a sinner like me?

