00:15:38,629 --> 00:15:45,950
♫  I can't hold onto my lover's heart, turning back, 
 I realize there is nowhere to go  ♫

184
00:15:45,950 --> 00:15:53,909
♫  The fireworks of the world are like quicksand 
 of the world after all  ♫

