00:15:53,909 --> 00:16:01,259
♫  In that moment of confusion, 
 I want to know what your answer will be  ♫

186
00:16:01,259 --> 00:16:08,139
♫  Again, someone on the precipice of fate 
 leaves tear stains behind while bidding farewell  ♫

187
00:16:08,153 --> 00:16:10,015
Shen Jinghong!

188
00:16:10,015 --> 00:16:12,634
♫  The world of mortals is lonely and painful  ♫

189
00:16:12,634 --> 00:16:14,615
Shen Jinghong, you're burning up.

190
00:16:14,615 --> 00:16:16,215
Wake up.

191
00:16:26,514 --> 00:16:27,694
Don't move.

192
00:16:27,694 --> 00:16:29,635
Do you want some medicine?

193
00:16:30,915 --> 00:16:32,334
My head hurts.

194
00:16:32,335 --> 00:16:33,453
It hurts?

195
00:16:33,454 --> 00:16:35,474
Do you want a massage?

196
00:16:38,895 --> 00:16:40,495
Take it slow.

197
00:16:45,495 --> 00:16:47,195
You're awake.

198
00:16:47,195 --> 00:16:49,214
Have some medicine.

199
00:16:53,635 --> 00:16:55,135
Why are you here?

200
00:16:55,135 --> 00:16:58,115
I walked right in.

201
00:16:58,115 --> 00:16:59,653
Your door was open.

202
00:16:59,654 --> 00:17:02,453
Also, if I didn't save you,

203
00:17:02,454 --> 00:17:04,633
you would have gotten brain damage from the fever.

204
00:17:04,633 --> 00:17:07,334
But why don't you have any servants at home?

205
00:17:07,335 --> 00:17:11,394
You were in the yard all night and nobody noticed.

206
00:17:12,974 --> 00:17:16,735
I wanted to be alone so I gave them a day off.

207
00:17:16,735 --> 00:17:18,453
Since you don't have servants now,

208
00:17:18,454 --> 00:17:21,234
all the more reason I should stay and look after you.

209
00:17:24,335 --> 00:17:26,334
Thank you for helping, Princess Jing'an.

210
00:17:26,335 --> 00:17:27,933
I'm fine now.

211
00:17:27,934 --> 00:17:29,814
Please return, Princess Jing'an.

212
00:17:30,375 --> 00:17:31,675
But...

213
00:17:32,855 --> 00:17:34,595
Don't move.

214
00:17:34,595 --> 00:17:37,094
Do you really want to get brain damage?

215
00:17:39,955 --> 00:17:41,654
It's none of your business. Right?

216
00:17:41,654 --> 00:17:43,355
You...

217
00:17:46,414 --> 00:17:47,814
Fine.

218
00:17:47,815 --> 00:17:50,715
Finish the medicine and I will leave.

219
00:17:50,715 --> 00:17:52,874
I will watch you finish it.

220
00:18:05,254 --> 00:18:06,954
Are you happy now?

221
00:18:20,295 --> 00:18:22,973
I'm a foreign princess,so I can be excused for my manners.

222
00:18:22,974 --> 00:18:26,595
Princess Roujia, shouldn't you be a precious and pure being?

223
00:18:26,595 --> 00:18:29,855
How can you come to a man's home in the morning?

224
00:18:30,535 --> 00:18:32,335
You've misunderstood, Jing'an.

225
00:18:32,335 --> 00:18:36,594
I'm here to meet Official Shen to discuss matters regarding Jishan Hall.

226
00:18:36,594 --> 00:18:38,534
Stop pretending.

227
00:18:38,535 --> 00:18:41,235
I'm not a fool who would believe you.

228
00:18:42,114 --> 00:18:43,173
Never mind.

229
00:18:43,174 --> 00:18:47,435
You're young and unfiltered, so I will not find fault with you.

230
00:18:47,435 --> 00:18:49,895
But don't go too far.

231
00:18:49,895 --> 00:18:54,515
Don't forget, your brother is concerned about you.

232
00:19:18,055 --> 00:19:19,755
Are you unwell?

233
00:19:31,955 --> 00:19:34,135
Why are you here, Your Highness?

234
00:19:34,135 --> 00:19:35,814
Please return.

235
00:19:35,814 --> 00:19:37,434
Why?

236
00:19:39,834 --> 00:19:43,795
My humble abode is unworthy of your presence.

237
00:20:34,535 --> 00:20:36,575
What are you doing?

238
00:20:37,174 --> 00:20:39,655
Lowering your temperature with alcohol.

239
00:20:44,615 --> 00:20:46,555
Don't worry about me, Your Highness.

240
00:20:47,454 --> 00:20:49,455
I'm much better now.

241
00:20:50,855 --> 00:20:52,455
Is that so?

242
00:20:53,014 --> 00:20:55,555
I see that your ears are still red

243
00:20:55,555 --> 00:20:57,634
so I thought you still had a fever.

244
00:21:03,014 --> 00:21:05,794
I know you're angry at me.

245
00:21:05,794 --> 00:21:09,755
I was a little harsh that day,

246
00:21:11,095 --> 00:21:15,635
but Sun Yunqian's death was a surprise to me.

247
00:21:16,174 --> 00:21:18,714
Of course, I knew you were friends.

248
00:21:18,714 --> 00:21:22,435
Even if I did not care about him, I cared about your feelings.

249
00:21:32,855 --> 00:21:34,974
After recovering,

250
00:21:36,254 --> 00:21:38,494
you should replenish your nutrients.

251
00:21:42,575 --> 00:21:45,314
Your Highness is precious,

252
00:21:45,314 --> 00:21:47,334
so you don't have to waste time here.

253
00:21:47,335 --> 00:21:50,014
Since you know Her Highness is precious,

254
00:21:50,014 --> 00:21:53,574
then you should know that Her Highness has never taken care of others like so.

255
00:21:53,575 --> 00:21:56,795
She even scalded her fingers to make soup for you.

256
