00:22:47,207 --> 00:22:54,847
♫  Again, someone on the precipice of fate 
 leaves tear stains behind while bidding farewell  ♫

263
00:22:54,847 --> 00:23:02,220
♫  The heartache is caused by the painful loneliness  ♫

264
00:23:02,220 --> 00:23:10,022
♫  The fireworks of the world are like quicksand 
 of the world after all  ♫

265
00:23:10,022 --> 00:23:17,687
♫  I cared about you with all my heart, 
 but how are you going to accept it?  ♫

266
00:23:17,687 --> 00:23:21,379
♫  The sound of the wind is like 
 the desperate cries from the jackdaw  ♫

267
00:23:21,383 --> 00:23:25,288
♫  This regret sprouts from the joys and sorrows  ♫

268
00:23:25,288 --> 00:23:32,483
♫  The city in my heart collapsed from the loneliness and pain  ♫

269
00:23:32,507 --> 00:23:39,579
♫  In the years of deep love, I am willing to shield you from the wind and sand  ♫

270
00:23:39,579 --> 00:23:42,382
   

271
00:23:42,974 --> 00:23:44,253
Official Mu,

272
00:23:44,254 --> 00:23:45,875
what do you think?

273
00:23:53,335 --> 00:23:54,735
Official Mu.

274
00:23:55,335 --> 00:23:57,475
Were you listening to me?

275
00:23:58,174 --> 00:24:01,455
Your Majesty, my apologies for my manners before the throne.

276
00:24:01,455 --> 00:24:03,435
No need to kneel.

277
00:24:04,794 --> 00:24:06,814
I was just asking.

278
00:24:07,734 --> 00:24:09,374
What is wrong with you today?

279
00:24:09,375 --> 00:24:12,135
You have been so restless.

280
00:24:13,254 --> 00:24:14,654
Your Majesty,

281
00:24:14,654 --> 00:24:16,815
my...

282
00:24:16,815 --> 00:24:21,195
my back is slightly aching.

283
00:24:21,195 --> 00:24:23,054
I don't feel quite well.

284
00:24:26,855 --> 00:24:31,234
I'm sure it's because you are worn out from working on the Talent Appreciation System.

285
00:24:35,174 --> 00:24:37,494
Summon an imperial physician.

286
00:24:38,454 --> 00:24:41,835
Your Majesty, I am afraid...

287
00:24:41,835 --> 00:24:45,013
that it's just a minor discomfort.

288
00:24:45,014 --> 00:24:46,313
I will get better in a few days.

289
00:24:46,313 --> 00:24:48,334
There is no need to summon an imperial physician.

290
00:24:48,335 --> 00:24:50,534
- It's just... 
 - Your Majesty.

291
00:24:50,535 --> 00:24:52,094
I'm fine, really.

292
00:24:52,095 --> 00:24:53,695
But...

293
00:24:57,254 --> 00:25:01,874
Your Majesty, in my opinion, I don't think Official Mu is unwell.

294
00:25:03,254 --> 00:25:05,054
If not, then what?

295
00:25:05,694 --> 00:25:08,695
Perhaps it's menstruation.

296
00:25:17,615 --> 00:25:19,634
Well, it's like that.

297
00:25:20,654 --> 00:25:22,254
I...

298
00:25:23,254 --> 00:25:25,554
I misunderstood.

299
00:25:28,855 --> 00:25:31,755
Well, why don't I give you half a day off?

300
00:25:31,755 --> 00:25:34,154
You may go home and rest.

301
00:25:34,815 --> 00:25:36,094
Thank you, Your Majesty.

302
00:25:36,095 --> 00:25:40,614
I shall complete my work at the Ministry of Revenue before I return home.

303
00:25:41,934 --> 00:25:43,213
Sure.

304
00:25:43,214 --> 00:25:45,335
You should take care.

305
00:25:47,135 --> 00:25:48,935
Don't overwork yourself.

306
00:25:50,535 --> 00:25:52,335
Yes.

307
00:25:52,335 --> 00:25:54,934
I shall take my leave, then.

308
00:25:59,775 --> 00:26:03,053
Your Majesty, please excuse me for being honest.

309
00:26:03,053 --> 00:26:04,634
   

310
00:26:04,634 --> 00:26:07,075
My greetings to you, Lord Ding.

311
00:26:12,135 --> 00:26:13,835
Thank you, My Lord.

312
00:26:18,174 --> 00:26:20,895
This is the palace carriage.

313
00:26:21,895 --> 00:26:24,574
His Majesty knew that I was unwell

314
00:26:24,575 --> 00:26:27,775
and fetched the palace carriage to send me home.

315
00:26:28,775 --> 00:26:31,054
His Majesty is so kind to you.

316
00:26:31,974 --> 00:26:33,493
His Majesty is kind to you, My Lord.

317
00:26:33,494 --> 00:26:35,414
I'm nothing compared to you.

318
00:26:38,414 --> 00:26:41,035
Is somebody being jealous?

319
00:26:41,035 --> 00:26:44,554
Oh, it's my man!

320
00:26:47,570 --> 00:26:49,890
   

321
00:26:49,895 --> 00:26:50,973
Grandaunt,

322
00:26:50,974 --> 00:26:53,454
can't you just stay in the capital?

323
00:26:53,454 --> 00:26:57,675
You should allow me to show my filialty to you.

324
00:26:57,675 --> 00:27:00,253
That's right. It's so far and distant.

325
00:27:00,253 --> 00:27:03,895
Once you depart from here, we won't know when we can meet again.

326
00:27:03,895 --> 00:27:06,054
I've lived in Jiangnan for too long.

327
00:27:06,054 --> 00:27:09,135
I'm not used to the capital's climate.

328
00:27:12,775 --> 00:27:16,775
Your Majesty is the emperor and has many responsibilities.

329
00:27:16,775 --> 00:27:20,495
I'm honored that you are here to bid me farewell.

330
00:27:20,495 --> 00:27:22,435
What do you mean?

331
00:27:22,435 --> 00:27:24,114
I am a junior.

332
00:27:24,114 --> 00:27:27,294
Juniors typically bid their elders farewell.

333
00:27:27,295 --> 00:27:29,175
I'm just doing what I should be.

334
00:27:29,175 --> 00:27:33,493
Ordinary people at your age

335
00:27:33,494 --> 00:27:36,254
would have already gotten married and had children.

336
00:27:36,254 --> 00:27:37,574
That's right.

337
00:27:37,575 --> 00:27:40,315
But nothing I say will work.

338
00:27:40,315 --> 00:27:44,254
His Majesty always gives excuses.

339
00:27:44,254 --> 00:27:46,294
Why are we talking about this?

340
00:27:50,694 --> 00:27:52,594
Your Majesty.

341
00:27:52,594 --> 00:27:55,294
Be honest with me.

342
00:27:55,295 --> 00:27:58,095
Do you have someone you like?

343
00:28:01,974 --> 00:28:03,774
How is that possible?

344
00:28:08,775 --> 00:28:12,854
It seems Liu Chen has feelings for Zhuohua.

345
00:28:12,854 --> 00:28:15,914
I noticed it when we were in Jiangnan.

346
00:28:17,454 --> 00:28:22,154
Will he lose focus on this

347
00:28:22,154 --> 00:28:26,675
and fall out with Liu Yan for her sake?

348
00:28:26,675 --> 00:28:29,654
You're so sharp, Your Highness.

349
00:28:34,135 --> 00:28:39,813
Speaking of which, a few days ago, I saw the female Tanhua of Southern Chen.

350
00:28:39,813 --> 00:28:41,795
She is very witty.

351
00:28:42,654 --> 00:28:44,554
That's right.

352
00:28:44,554 --> 00:28:48,614
Zhuohua is talented and not inferior to men.

353
00:28:55,615 --> 00:28:57,474
You're a young lady now.

354
00:28:57,474 --> 00:28:59,614
Why are you acting cute

355
00:28:59,614 --> 00:29:02,335
like when you were younger?

356
00:29:03,414 --> 00:29:05,414
Grandaunt,

357
00:29:05,414 --> 00:29:08,175
I would like to ask for something from you.

358
00:29:08,175 --> 00:29:11,275
What's mine is yours.

359
00:29:11,275 --> 00:29:17,594
Even if you want the stars of the sky, I will try to get them for you.

360
00:29:18,535 --> 00:29:22,335
Grandaunt, can you give me the Evil-erasing Sword?

361
00:29:24,815 --> 00:29:28,854
The Evil-erasing Sword is a national weapon.

362
00:29:28,854 --> 00:29:33,874
It can only appear when the country is in danger.

363
00:29:33,874 --> 00:29:35,774
Noble families are in power.

364
00:29:35,775 --> 00:29:38,955
Is this not a sign of a dying country?

365
00:29:40,174 --> 00:29:41,774
Jiaojiao,

366
00:29:41,774 --> 00:29:46,594
since when have you been interested in political matters?

367
00:29:49,375 --> 00:29:51,715
I am also of royal blood.

368
00:29:51,715 --> 00:29:54,375
It is only normal for me to be concerned

369
00:29:54,375 --> 00:29:56,695
about the national matters of Southern Chen.

370
00:29:56,695 --> 00:29:59,074
Normal?

371
00:30:03,174 --> 00:30:04,574
Jiaojiao,

372
00:30:05,615 --> 00:30:10,015
could it be that you wish to take that seat?

373
00:30:11,295 --> 00:30:12,795
Grandaunt.

374
00:30:13,974 --> 00:30:18,573
Did you not teach me all this knowledge on governance for national stability?

375
00:30:19,295 --> 00:30:24,994
You should know very well that I am more capable than Liu Chen.

376
00:30:24,994 --> 00:30:28,294
If I become the empress, it will bless the people.

377
00:30:31,575 --> 00:30:33,695
I taught you such things

378
00:30:33,695 --> 00:30:36,654
so that you would have a sense of discernment.

379
00:30:36,654 --> 00:30:40,415
I did not expect to encourage such ideas.

380
00:30:41,895 --> 00:30:45,055
What is wrong with having these ideas?

381
00:30:45,055 --> 00:30:46,735
Jiaojiao,

382
00:30:46,735 --> 00:30:49,914
that is a road of no return.

383
00:30:49,914 --> 00:30:51,814
While it seems noble and glorified,

384
00:30:51,815 --> 00:30:53,894
it is actually like walking on thin ice.

385
00:30:53,895 --> 00:30:55,894
You cannot lower your guard for even an instance.

386
00:30:55,895 --> 00:30:58,535
Only an incapable ruler would walk on thin ice.

387
00:31:00,895 --> 00:31:05,095
I will definitely be a wise ruler who is loved by the country.

388
00:31:06,974 --> 00:31:08,674
Jiaojiao,

389
00:31:09,414 --> 00:31:11,895
you've had a rough childhood.

390
00:31:11,895 --> 00:31:15,315
I cannot bear to see you take such risks.

391
00:31:15,855 --> 00:31:20,494
I just hope to see you live happily as the First Princess of Southern Chen.

392
00:31:30,775 --> 00:31:32,275
Grandaunt,

393
00:31:33,295 --> 00:31:35,835
but I only want that seat.

394
00:31:37,055 --> 00:31:39,594
If you really care about me,

395
00:31:39,615 --> 00:31:42,174
give me the Evil-erasing Sword.

396
00:31:47,895 --> 00:31:50,194
Impossible.

397
00:31:52,454 --> 00:31:54,254
Jiaojiao,

398
00:31:54,254 --> 00:31:57,013
why would you have such ideas?

399
00:31:57,014 --> 00:32:00,034
Just forget about it. This is impossible!

400
00:32:04,454 --> 00:32:07,335
Grandaunt, calm down.

401
00:32:25,895 --> 00:32:28,434
Grandaunt, calm down.

402
00:32:28,434 --> 00:32:30,775
It's my fault,

403
00:32:30,815 --> 00:32:32,874
don't be angry anymore.

404
00:32:48,654 --> 00:32:50,054
Jiaojiao,

405
00:32:50,055 --> 00:32:51,973
return to Jiangzuo with me.

406
00:32:51,974 --> 00:32:53,453
We will live a peaceful life.

407
00:32:53,454 --> 00:32:54,754
Okay?

408
00:32:55,495 --> 00:32:57,913
- Listen to me. 
 - Grandaunt.

409
00:32:58,654 --> 00:33:01,454
I will not return to Jiangzuo with you.

410
00:33:01,454 --> 00:33:04,114
I just want to tend to you in the capital.

411
00:33:07,874 --> 00:33:10,795
Why am I feeling dizzy?

412
00:33:19,295 --> 00:33:21,195
Jiaojiao.

413
00:33:23,275 --> 00:33:25,875
You drugged me?

414
00:33:27,775 --> 00:33:30,075
Grandaunt,

415
00:33:30,075 --> 00:33:32,695
this drug is harmless.

416
00:33:34,174 --> 00:33:36,774
It will only make you weak.

417
00:33:38,734 --> 00:33:41,775
I would never hurt you.

418
00:33:48,096 --> 00:33:49,905
   

419
00:33:50,515 --> 00:33:52,715
Qi.

420
00:33:53,694 --> 00:33:55,954
Look at you.

421
00:33:55,954 --> 00:34:00,595
Those who know what happened would know that you requested Qi to do the Mu family a favor.

422
00:34:00,595 --> 00:34:03,314
But those who don't would think you're unwilling to part with her.

423
00:34:03,314 --> 00:34:07,714
Why are you pointing it out?

424
00:34:09,295 --> 00:34:12,413
Mother. Old Master Mu.

425
00:34:12,413 --> 00:34:16,855
Since His Majesty has made the judgment, it's time to wrap it up.

426
00:34:16,855 --> 00:34:21,274
In the future, if we just do as we're told,

427
00:34:21,274 --> 00:34:23,575
there will be nothing to worry about.

428
00:34:23,575 --> 00:34:26,434
Don't worry. I will keep an eye on him.

429
00:34:27,594 --> 00:34:32,314
Even if I can't do it myself, I have 18 sisters to help me out.

430
00:34:47,255 --> 00:34:50,895
Qi, I don't mean to lecture you.

431
00:34:50,895 --> 00:34:55,554
Though I'm quite the playboy, I gave every concubine the acknowledgment they deserved.

432
00:34:55,554 --> 00:34:57,834
They are all part of the Mu family.

433
00:34:57,834 --> 00:35:01,814
But you are even worse than I am.

434
00:35:01,814 --> 00:35:04,854
Can't you even acknowledge him?

435
00:35:05,855 --> 00:35:09,975
Such behavior is really unfair.

436
00:35:09,975 --> 00:35:11,875
So, you're fair?

437
00:35:11,875 --> 00:35:14,834
But our home is running out of space.

438
00:35:14,834 --> 00:35:18,855
Do you think Qi cannot see what kind of player you are?

439
00:35:18,855 --> 00:35:22,475
You want to be the Prince Regent's father-in-law, don't you?

440
00:35:22,475 --> 00:35:24,394
Stop calling me out.

441
00:35:24,394 --> 00:35:28,174
Enough, let's go or we won't reach the lodging in time.

442
00:35:28,175 --> 00:35:30,075
We'll get going, then.

443
00:35:31,314 --> 00:35:35,134
Qi, you are meant to do great things.

444
00:35:35,134 --> 00:35:37,335
The Mu family is unable to support you,

445
00:35:37,335 --> 00:35:39,314
but don't worry, you have me.

446
00:35:39,314 --> 00:35:41,775
They will not cause you more trouble.

447
00:35:41,775 --> 00:35:44,815
Just walk forward fearlessly.

448
00:35:44,815 --> 00:35:46,575
Thank you, Mother.

449
00:36:10,182 --> 00:36:14,332
♫  The flowing water bends and reflects the round moon  ♫

450
00:36:14,332 --> 00:36:16,394
♫  Gently sprinkling your eyebrows and eyes  ♫

451
00:36:16,394 --> 00:36:18,714
Let me do it myself.

452
00:36:18,714 --> 00:36:21,174
- Delicious, right? 
 - Delicious.

453
00:36:25,382 --> 00:36:29,402
♫  The night rain hitting the sycamore tree disturbs a sparrow  ♫

454
00:36:29,402 --> 00:36:33,182
♫  The young maiden become acquainted with 
 the green robes in that moment  ♫

455
00:36:34,775 --> 00:36:36,654
What's wrong?

456
00:36:39,622 --> 00:36:41,883
   

457
00:36:42,795 --> 00:36:44,334
Would you like a steamed bun?

458
00:36:44,334 --> 00:36:48,282
♫  ...stretching while not breaking my time and drifting away  ♫

459
00:36:48,282 --> 00:36:54,112
♫  Thousands of words are not enough 
 to accompany the long journey  ♫

460
00:36:54,112 --> 00:36:58,802
Since it is your treat, we should at least go to Yipin Bakery.

461
00:37:00,695 --> 00:37:03,114
When I have ever starved you?

462
00:37:03,114 --> 00:37:10,232
♫  Accompanying you, calmly waiting 
 for the clouds to fade away  ♫

463
00:37:11,679 --> 00:37:12,954
   

464
00:37:14,414 --> 00:37:16,254
I was thinking of getting a free meal

465
00:37:16,255 --> 00:37:18,781
but I didn't expect it to be sold out.

466
00:37:21,014 --> 00:37:23,613
My Lord, shall we go to Shixiang House?

467
00:37:23,614 --> 00:37:27,913
I heard from Juli that they hired a good chef who's skilled in pastries.

468
00:37:27,913 --> 00:37:29,401
Sure.

469
00:37:29,402 --> 00:37:33,231
♫  Toiling away long hours together with the candle's light  ♫

470
00:37:33,232 --> 00:37:36,882
♫  Not caring about the high mountains, deep waters, and long roads  ♫

471
00:37:36,882 --> 00:37:43,482
♫  Fortunately, you are here, not afraid of the repeated trips 
 and hanging around with me  ♫

472
00:37:43,482 --> 00:37:51,852
♫  You are like the flowers and moon, stretching while unbroken my time and drifting away  ♫

473
00:37:51,852 --> 00:37:58,502
♫  Thousands of words are not enough 
 to accompany the long journey  ♫

474
00:37:58,502 --> 00:38:06,782
♫  You are like the flowers and moon, 
 more graceful than a palace in the sky  ♫

475
00:38:06,782 --> 00:38:11,214
 Should I acknowledge him? 

476
00:38:23,775 --> 00:38:25,694
This hairpin is luxurious.

477
00:38:25,695 --> 00:38:28,734
If other women wear it, it would outshine them.

478
00:38:28,734 --> 00:38:30,474
Only you can match up to it, Yunyun.

479
00:38:30,474 --> 00:38:33,214
As expected of a most outstanding noble lady.

480
00:38:37,255 --> 00:38:40,633
I'm sorry. That was rude of me.

481
00:38:40,633 --> 00:38:43,214
You shouldn't say that, Your Highness.

482
00:38:43,214 --> 00:38:45,554
You are my savior.

483
00:38:45,554 --> 00:38:48,734
I am so grateful to you, Your Highness.

484
00:38:48,734 --> 00:38:50,613
Every injustice has its perpetrator.

485
00:38:50,614 --> 00:38:53,414
I will make sure Mu Zhuohua pays for it.

486
00:38:54,275 --> 00:38:58,394
Zhuohua may have her reasons.

487
00:39:00,114 --> 00:39:03,814
Never mind. If you have any troubles,

488
00:39:03,815 --> 00:39:07,975
just let me know and I will help you as much as I can.

489
00:39:09,074 --> 00:39:11,074
Thank you, Your Highness.

490
00:39:17,594 --> 00:39:19,894
Jing'an, you're back?

491
00:39:19,894 --> 00:39:22,694
You look very happy.

492
00:39:22,694 --> 00:39:26,255
I presume you enjoyed yourself.

493
00:39:26,255 --> 00:39:30,235
I'd be happy doing anything as long as I'm with Official Shen.

494
00:39:33,274 --> 00:39:35,593
Princess Jing'an has been in Southern Chen for a while now,

495
00:39:35,593 --> 00:39:38,093
yet your manners are still lacking.

496
00:39:38,094 --> 00:39:40,573
I'm afraid you're overly focused on romance

497
00:39:40,574 --> 00:39:42,914
and overlooked your priorities.

498
00:39:44,414 --> 00:39:49,214
I wonder who has been crushing on the Prince Regent for years

499
00:39:49,214 --> 00:39:52,294
and eventually became a maiden.

500
00:39:52,294 --> 00:39:55,515
You fight every time you meet.

501
00:39:55,515 --> 00:39:59,394
We are family. We should live in harmony together.

502
00:39:59,394 --> 00:40:01,775
Who are you calling family?

503
00:40:09,255 --> 00:40:11,575
You have skin as smooth as porcelain.

504
00:40:12,414 --> 00:40:17,074
I'm sure these pearls will make you even more dazzling.

505
00:40:23,215 --> 00:40:26,695
Yunyun is not completely wrong.

506
00:40:26,695 --> 00:40:28,573
The Mid-Autumn Palace Banquet is tomorrow.

507
00:40:28,574 --> 00:40:31,114
You must be careful to guard your dignity.

508
00:40:31,114 --> 00:40:35,433
After all, you didn't come to Southern Chen just for sightseeing and leisure.

509
00:40:36,514 --> 00:40:39,413
All right. I shall excuse myself.

510
00:40:59,895 --> 00:41:01,795
Grandaunt,

511
00:41:02,795 --> 00:41:04,894
I know you're awake.

512
00:41:05,955 --> 00:41:08,655
Do you dislike seeing me so much?

513
00:41:21,554 --> 00:41:23,454
Grandaunt.

514
00:41:25,574 --> 00:41:28,334
I'm your beloved Jiaojiao.

515
00:41:29,095 --> 00:41:35,755
Did you not say that you would even give me the stars of the sky?

516
00:41:37,314 --> 00:41:42,195
Now, I am only asking for the Evil-erasing Sword.

517
00:41:43,014 --> 00:41:45,615
Why won't you give it to me?

518
00:41:46,974 --> 00:41:48,874
"Only"?

519
00:41:51,414 --> 00:41:56,315
When civil unrest begins, poverty will strike.

